Author: bumbumboleji
Text: Aww hun..how about just going vegan again? I don’t get the hate that people sometimes give restrictive habits..it’s got to be better for you than b/p right? As long as you are having something nutritious   I know I feel way way better restricting than b/p and b/p is freakin hard to stop it’s almost addictive in some ways   Wish you all the best
